<br>
Pottery: Casserole dish @199 <br>
Baking: Patty Melt @191 (I was forgetting the noodles in the various @250+ casseroles)<br>
Brewing: Mino Brew @248 (bah! 2 off!)<br>
Smithing: Platinum Ornate Chain @162<br>
Tailoring: Picnic Basket @70 (I was thinking the @187 LoY ribbons didn't have the foraged bits)<br>
Fletching: Shadewood-hemp Bow @250<br>
Poison: Spirit of Sloth @250<br>
Alchemy: Mystical Endurance (or 5 others) @250<br>
<br>
So, there are the figures, straight from EQtraders.<br>
